{"tid":1059210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日防衛相：美軍機可在「出雲」號上加油及維護","createTime":"2019-03-13T03:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T11:47:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"219225e6fa055820a77aec8ce2e2656080c75525","tid":1059210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"圍繞實際上將改裝為航母的日本海上自衛隊護衛艦「出雲」號的運用方式，防衛相岩屋毅8日在眾院安全保障委員會會議上表示，他認為在艦上為美軍戰鬥機加油及維護不存在法律上的問題。他明確表示，「對於滿足安全保障相關法的必要條件、符合國家利益在艦上降落的美國軍機，進行加油和維修是可能的」。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，岩屋對在野黨議員宮本徹的提問進行答辯，當被問到美國軍機是否有可能參與空襲時，岩屋稱「不排除」這一可能。宮本批評稱「這樣一來，&lsquo;出雲&rsquo;號無疑就是《憲法》規定不可擁有的攻擊型航母」。在野黨或將主張其違憲、加強追究。<br />\n<br />\n有關改裝後的「出雲」號，岩屋說明稱「能力上將使美軍擁有的F-35B戰機起降成為可能」。有關F-35B的加油和維護，岩屋稱「一般來說，法律上是可能的。至於會主動進行何種支援，是根據事態、在國會的參與下作出決定的事項」。F-35B是有著卓越隱形性能的最尖端戰機，可短距起飛及垂直降落，可用於航母作戰。<br />\n<br />\n有關是否實施美軍F-35B的艦上起降訓練，岩屋強調：「包括在外交上何種舉措才妥當在內，將進行綜合判斷。並不是說（F-35B）絕對不能上日本的護衛艦上。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4085918-%E6%97%A5%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E7%9B%B8%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%B2%E3%80%8D%E8%99%9F%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9%E5%8F%8A%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7?current_cat=157278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F4085918-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%259B%25B8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%259B%25B2%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%2599%259F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%3Fcurrent_cat%3D157278&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=605f3537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4085918-%E6%97%A5%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E7%9B%B8%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%B2%E3%80%8D%E8%99%9F%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9%E5%8F%8A%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7?current_cat=157278</a>"},{"pid":"be2f9339b7fb38bf49b117249e48905d3fe794ba","tid":1059210,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:49:24.000Z","msg":"贏國反應呢"},{"pid":"0948f611ba2efdf559305fd489ed545576640b6a","tid":1059210,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"真。美軍來了我帶路"},{"pid":"0d6b2b7e8443b6632b89fc8a0f0f7873843ed63f","tid":1059210,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"非攻擊型F35咪得"},{"pid":"6f59e3a893d80a48aaf888ab2b87c25182f77751","tid":1059210,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"出雲 唔係沉左咩？"},{"pid":"57ac70b39fc2ec32c8f859cf2b95edd992de0a67","tid":1059210,"uid":8105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc4b69a1c5a4480f6ea5e32d5de9a0722d8d56e","tid":1059210,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f59e3a893d80a48aaf888ab2b87c25182f77751","tid":1059210,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"出雲 唔係沉左咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"你昏迷左幾多年？"},{"pid":"e7b5ee27e6b3099943cb0ae3f06c31e5b8dba4a4","tid":1059210,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc4b69a1c5a4480f6ea5e32d5de9a0722d8d56e","tid":1059210,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f59e3a893d80a48aaf888ab2b87c25182f77751","tid":1059210,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"出雲 唔係沉左咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"你昏迷左幾多年？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"美國隊長果年 打九頭蛇"},{"pid":"b23368c6ec64c2102ae019699f07727b7b428ab1","tid":1059210,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019